N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 320.3 - Recommended forms

State Regulations

The term recommended forms applies to those forms which
are supplied by the department, but whose use is not required. Local equivalent
of such forms shall not be subject to approval by the
department. Notes
